title: SpaceboyTF
author: SpaceboyTF
content: As we all already know SBF, the FTX CEO had revealed that he is a significant donor in both D and R primaries. Well due to the election day, it might be one of the reason that caused the price of the FTT such volatile. And of course the news from CZ / Binance acquire FTX was the another reason too. What do you think? Correct me if I'm wrong
